Write a polymorphic java program to find the area of rectangle, circle, square and triangle. Use following function definition:

double area(double a,double b)                  //rectangle,square

double area(double r)                           //circle

double area(double a,double b,double c)         //triangle

Enter your choice :1
Enter length :3.5
Enter breadth :2.9
Area of rectangle is :10.15
 

Enter your choice :2
Enter edge :5.5
Area of square is :30.25
 

Enter your choice :3
Enter radius :4.5
Area of circle is :63.585
 

Enter your choice :4
Enter side 1 :2
Enter side 2 :3
Enter side 3 :4
Area of triangle is :2.9047375096555625
